@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
<p class="text-muted">Last updated: @DateTime.Now.ToString("MMMM yyyy")</p>

<hr />

<h5>Data We Collect</h5>
<p>The Flight Management System collects the following personal data to process flight bookings:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Full name and contact information</li>
    <li>Passport number and date of birth</li>
    <li>Payment information (processed securely)</li>
    <li>Booking and reservation history</li>
</ul>

<h5>How We Use Your Data</h5>
<p>Your data is used solely for the purpose of managing flight reservations and providing customer support. We do not share your data with third parties except where required to process payments.</p>

<h5>Data Security</h5>
<p>All personal data is stored securely and protected in accordance with standard data protection practices. Passwords are hashed and never stored in plain text.</p>

<h5>Contact</h5>
<p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at support@flightmanagementsystem.com</p>